<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Panpihtu Nai Zing</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa, Na vanglim nuoiah,
 Chawlhdamna nuom a um;
 Na theihna in buoina tincheng,
 Apat ei puidawk in.

[V2]
 Na lungkham A kawmah tunin,
 Na lungkham A kawmah tunin;
 Na lungkham A kawmah tunin,
 Aman hun na panpih zel ina.

[V3]
 2. Na kienga thil ka hun tut cheng,
 Kipak takin nei dawng;
 Lungngaih thavaih, buoina tin cheng,
 Dahumna cheng cheng tawh.

[V4]
 3. Bangdi'n lungkham na'n I dim dem,
 Dahumna hung tun tieng?
 Ginglote lauin, ling un au,
 I kipah niu a chun.</lyrics>
<author>S.S 878</author>
<hymn_number>132</hymn_number>
</song>